##[[一日]]
##*(いちにち, ''ichinichi''): one day
##*(ついたち, ''tsuitachi''): first day of the month
##[[二日]] (ふつか, ''futsuka''): two days, second day of the month
##[[三日]] (みっか, ''mikka''): three days, third day of the month
##[[四日]] (よっか, ''yokka''): four days, fourth day of the month
##[[五日]] (いつか, ''itsuka''): five days, fifth day of the month
##[[六日]] (むいか, ''muika''): six days, sixth day of the month
##[[七日]] (なのか, ''nanoka''): seven days, seventh day of the month
##[[八日]] (ようか, ''yōka''): eight days, eighth day of the month
##[[九日]] (ここのか, ''kokonoka''): nine days, ninth day of the month
##[[十日]] (とおか, ''tōka''): ten days, tenth day of the month
##[[十一日]] (じゅういちにち, ''jūichinichi''): eleven days, eleventh day of the month
##[[十二日]] (じゅうににち, ''jūninichi''): twelve days, twelfth day of the month
##[[十三日]] (じゅうさんにち, ''jūsannichi''): thirteen days, thirteenth day of the month
##[[十四日]] (じゅうよっか, ''jūyokka'' or じゅうよにち, ''jūyonichi''): fourteen days, fourteenth day of the month
##[[十五日]] (じゅうごにち, ''jūgonichi''): fifteen days, fifteenth day of the month
##[[十六日]] (じゅうろくにち, ''jūrokunichi''): sixteen days, sixteenth day of the month
##[[十七日]] (じゅうしちにち, ''jūshichinichi'' or じゅうななにち, ''jūnananichi''): seventeen days, seventeenth day of the month
