##[[十九日]] (じゅうくにち, ''jūkunichi'' or じゅうきゅうにち, ''jūkyūnichi''): nineteen days, nineteenth day of the month
##[[二十日]] (はつか, ''hatsuka''): twenty days, twentieth day of the month
##[[二十一日]] (にじゅういちにち, ''nijūichinichi): twenty-one days, twenty-first day of the month
